high_descs: Move to the right toward the center island.
Pick up the lettuce from the island.
Bring the lettuce to the sink.
Put the lettuce in the sink and get it wet.
Pick up the lettuce and bring it to the center island.
Put the lettuce on the island next to the mug.
anns.task_desc: Wash the lettuce, put it back on the island.

high_descs: Walk forward, then turn left to face the counter.
Grab the head of lettuce that's in front of a ladle.
Turn left, than turn right, then turn left again to reach the sink.
Wash the lettuce in the sink, then pick it up again.
Turn around, then walk to table across from the fridge.
Place the lettuce on the table, to the right of the white mug and in front of the pepper.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed head of lettuce on a table.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the table.
Pick up the lettuce from the table.
Turn left and walk to the sink.
Rinse the lettuce off in the sink.
Turn around and walk to the side of the table with a stool in front of it.
Put the lettuce down on the table to the right of the cup.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned lettuce on the table.
